  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.6">
<l>paṇṇēr moḻiyāyc ciyarañ cavañcap pakuvāyk kaḻutuk kiraṅkā tavaḷtaṉ</l>
<l>uṇṇā mulaimaṟ ṟavaḷā viyōṭu muṭaṉē cuvaittā niṭamōṅ kupaintāḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṇār karumpiṉ kaḻaitiṉ ṟuvaikik kaḻunī rilmūḻkic ceḻunīrt taṭattu</l>
<l>maṇṇēn tiḷamē tikaḷvai kunāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nānkūr where young buffalos,</l>
<l rend="indent">having lingered munching on many-jointed, soaring sugarcane stalks,</l>
<l>Sinking among the waterlilies, linger in the pond of fertile water,</l>
<l rend="indent">[all] mud-covered,</l>
<l>The place of him who, being without pity for the deguised,</l>
<l rend="indent">gaping-mouthed demoness,</l>
<l>Consumed her inedible breasts, besides her life, all at once,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the herdess with speech suited to music was frightened.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
